A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Consumer Protection – Solicitation Following a Disaster – Prohibition
3 FOR the purpose of prohibiting a contractor or person acting on behalf of a contractor from
4 soliciting or attempting to solicit a disaster victim within a certain period of time
5 after a disaster; establishing that a violation of this Act is an unfair, abusive, or
6 deceptive trade practice; and generally relating to solicitation following a disaster.
